    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The Speech Synthesis Manager calls a speech channelâ€™s synchronizationcallback function whenever it encounters a synchronization commandembedded in a text buffer. You might use the synchronization callbackfunction to provide a callback not ordinarily provided. For example,you might inset synchronization commands at the end of every sentencein a text buffer, or you might enter synchronization commands afterevery numeric value in the text. However, to synchronize your applicationwith phonemes or words, it makes more sense to use the built-inphoneme and word callback functions, defined in ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/applicationservices/speechphonemeprocptr",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can specify a synchronization callback function by passingthe ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "soSyncCallBack",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " selector tothe ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "SetSpeechInfo",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " functionand embedding a synchronization command within a text buffer passedto the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "SpeakText",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " or ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "SpeakBuffer",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " function. ",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
